OL,4,Ccould set precedent for other ITV
OL,5,Cregions
OL,7,GOfcom's decision on STV's proposal to
OL,8,Gstop providing a distinct news service
OL,9,Gfor the north of Scotland could set a
OL,10,Gprecedent.
OL,12,FIf the STV North service goes, it
OL,13,Fwould be hard to refuse any requests
OL,14,Ffor similar changes to English regions.
OL,16,FSTV's plan is to produce a single news
OL,17,Fprogramme for both Central and
OL,18,FNorthern Scotland.
OL,20,FOfcom will need to approve the plan `
OL,21,Fit could potentially block it or
OL,22,Fsecure modifications.
