OL,7,FThere is no suggestion at present of
OL,8,Fimminent cuts but the point remains `
OL,9,Fadvertising is down and every cross-
OL,10,Fsubsidy will have to be considered
OL,11,Fsooner or later.
OL,13,FOnce a decision is taken to
OL,14,Feffectively scrap an official channel
OL,15,F3 region ` i.e., Grampian ` how can a
OL,16,Frequest to scrap another be flatly
OL,17,Frejected? And sub-regions are
OL,18,Fespecially vulnerable.
OL,20,FA proper debate is necessary on what
OL,21,Fsort of news service is sustainable on
OL,22,FChannel 3 going forward.
